{"tid":2491402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"贊助商諷刺熱刺無冠","createTime":"2021-04-16T09:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T18:03:05.000Z","uid":31314,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f887bc1c0edab760036bb1fc70e67ec8ff7a4714","tid":2491402,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://sportsmintmedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Dulux-becomes-Official-Paint-Supplier-to-Tottenham-Hotspur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsportsmintmedia.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FDulux-becomes-Official-Paint-Supplier-to-Tottenham-Hotspur.jpg&h=dee84d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱刺的新贊助商也許創下新河，周四早上宣佈合作，早上11點不到就要正式道歉。熱刺新球場剛使用不久，也許還很需要大量油漆，周四早上就宣佈與著名油漆品牌合作，可惜在熱刺宣佈的聲明上，該公司網站編輯就衰多手要道歉。話說有網民指熱刺是時候用贊助商的產品將球隊的獎盃櫃重新上漆，但新贊助商就回應：「<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">未用過的獎盃櫃出售中</span></span></strong>」；而有球迷指「塵封獎盃櫃」是時候好好用油漆粉飾一下時，新贊助商則回應：「<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">別做蠢事！有塵的表面是不能上漆的啊！</span></span></strong>」似乎對諷刺熱刺無冠不遺餘力。  <br />\n<br />\n至於熱刺放上該品牌的英國古代牧羊犬，<strong><span class=\"red\">結果有球迷留言：「狗狗可否打中堅？」該油漆公司官方Twitter編輯回應：「可能牠表現會更好！」</span></strong>以上諷刺熱刺的回應十分注目，不久就馬上刪除，但當然為時已晚。結果，油漆公司早上11點未到就要出帖道歉：「我們為今早的帖真誠致歉，這無改我們為成為熱刺贊助商的榮幸。我們正尋找原因，並向所有熱刺球迷道歉。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.sportbible.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=720,quality=70,format=jpeg,fit=pad,dpr=1/https%3A%2F%2Fs3-images.sportbible.com%2Fs3%2Fcontent%2F9f98ede860784fe3c7e9fa42292ded62.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportbible.com%2Fcdn-cgi%2Fimage%2Fwidth%3D720%2Cquality%3D70%2Cformat%3Djpeg%2Cfit%3Dpad%2Cdpr%3D1%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fs3-images.sportbible.com%252Fs3%252Fcontent%252F9f98ede860784fe3c7e9fa42292ded62.png&h=927c64ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"171d609e0ecd88ed0215f5b9d17611ec727885b0","tid":2491402,"uid":31314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.sportbible.com/cdn-cgi/image/height=700,quality=70,format=jpeg,fit=cover,dpr=1/https%3A%2F%2Fs3-images.sportbible.com%2Fs3%2Fcontent%2F540195146078425a952f990517b73fe8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportbible.com%2Fcdn-cgi%2Fimage%2Fheight%3D700%2Cquality%3D70%2Cformat%3Djpeg%2Cfit%3Dcover%2Cdpr%3D1%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fs3-images.sportbible.com%252Fs3%252Fcontent%252F540195146078425a952f990517b73fe8.png&h=313088ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9649aabccf14bb5d23c195c21eade1d571a546d5","tid":2491402,"uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://talksport.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2021/04/EzAI7pnXEAEHaDI.jpeg?strip=all&amp;w=960&amp;quality=100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftalksport.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F5%2F2021%2F04%2FEzAI7pnXEAEHaDI.jpeg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26w%3D960%26quality%3D100&h=c5bb8647&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8825ddfb2310e27fc2b336fb2ec8961ff5e1f43a","tid":2491402,"uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/HIQUz-h1stnJQmgFyd8pXh0V4-lMFjvKSXPVOTm4_OBzMRAw7oznVWjCu-WQSjjRx6ZglQBqagg70uJOtsuSxEjk70ZdkE_MVVdLn6TofMypFLaambIOaiL74OlXjoiAnswLk7yYiVw1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FHIQUz-h1stnJQmgFyd8pXh0V4-lMFjvKSXPVOTm4_OBzMRAw7oznVWjCu-WQSjjRx6ZglQBqagg70uJOtsuSxEjk70ZdkE_MVVdLn6TofMypFLaambIOaiL74OlXjoiAnswLk7yYiVw1&h=a4c44b69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c491c4e0acc3617cd92e1fc17dc7f705b6c69b1","tid":2491402,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:50:59.000Z","msg":"班白垃圾係咪唔識傑志？"},{"pid":"13ec7b629dd77e863f7703ed7c0695f4e590f394","tid":2491402,"uid":46013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma